52
00:04:59,049 --> 00:05:00,209
Te quedarás aquí.

53
00:05:06,649 --> 00:05:08,649
Szofia, llévalo a su celda.

54
00:05:08,729 --> 00:05:10,609
Achille, ve al blog de Alex

55
00:05:10,689 --> 00:05:13,729
y averigua quiénes descargaron el libro.

56
00:05:13,809 --> 00:05:14,889
Estás bromeando.

57
00:05:15,249 --> 00:05:16,529
